{
  "version": 2,
  "name": "Metallic Glass",
  "description": "Y2K-aesthetic feedback-displacement metallic surface generator, decomposed from the legacy MetallicGlassGenerator into curated primitives.\n\nPipeline: 3D simplex noise drives a feedback-blend loop (mix Difference + abs + mix Lerp at 0.98) that builds an evolving liquid-mercury height field; two-axis Gaussian blur smooths the result; the same height field feeds (a) a height/levels chain for the displacement R channel, (b) a mirror_axis → Sobel-magnitude chain for the metallic/edge G+B channels, and (c) per-pixel finite-difference normals inside the renderer for full-resolution reflections. A 0.15 temporal-blend feedback on the packed material texture eliminates per-frame jitter. The mesh path is the standard generate_grid_mesh → displace_mesh → triangulate_grid → render_3d_mesh_pbr_ibl chain; the env_map comes from bake_equirect_envmap (the procedural HDR studio).\n\nNew primitives shipped alongside this preset (all reusable):\n  - clamp_texture        — saturate atom\n  - mirror_axis          — single-axis mirror across an angled line\n  - cook_torrance_specular — sibling to blinn_specular (OilyFluid upgrade candidate)\n  - equirect_envmap_sample — IBL atom\n  - bake_equirect_envmap   — procedural HDR studio env baker\n  - pack_channels        — recompose RGBA from 4 single-channel textures\n  - render_3d_mesh_pbr_ibl — render-family entry parallel to render_3d_mesh (Lambert)\n\nKnown parity deltas vs legacy:\n(1) Sobel decomposes via brightness → convolution_2d_9tap ×2 → pack_channels → length_vec2 rather than the fused luma-Sobel in the legacy WGSL — boundary handling at the texture edges differs by ≤1 ULP per pixel.\n(2) The luma weights (Rec.601: 0.299/0.587/0.114) match exactly; the kernel weights match exactly; gradient_mag = sqrt(gx² + gy²) matches exactly.\n(3) Per-pixel normals inside the render shader come from sampling the packed material's R channel — identical math to the legacy fragment shader.",
  "presetMetadata": {
    "id": "MetallicGlass",
    "displayName": "Metallic Glass",
    "category": "Generator",
    "oscPrefix": "metallicGlass",
    "legacyDiscriminant": 23,
    "available": true,
    "params": [
      { "id": "feedback",    "name": "Feedback",         "min": 0.5,    "max": 1.0,    "defaultValue": 0.98,  "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F2" },
      { "id": "noise_scale", "name": "Noise Scale",      "min": 0.1,    "max": 2.0,    "defaultValue": 0.75,  "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F2" },
      { "id": "noise_speed", "name": "Noise Speed",      "min": 0.01,   "max": 1.0,    "defaultValue": 0.1,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F3" },
      { "id": "edge_str",    "name": "Edge Strength",    "min": 0.5,    "max": 20.0,   "defaultValue": 5.0,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F1" },
      { "id": "mirror",      "name": "Mirror",           "min": 0.0,    "max": 90.0,   "defaultValue": 45.0,  "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F0" },
      { "id": "displace",    "name": "Displace",         "min": 0.0,    "max": 0.5,    "defaultValue": 0.2,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F3" },
      { "id": "roughness",   "name": "Roughness",        "min": 0.01,   "max": 1.0,    "defaultValue": 0.05,  "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F3" },
      { "id": "light_int",   "name": "Light Intensity",  "min": 0.1,    "max": 10.0,   "defaultValue": 3.5,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F1" },
      { "id": "cam_dist",    "name": "Camera Distance",  "min": 0.5,    "max": 10.0,   "defaultValue": 2.5,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F2" },
      { "id": "cam_orbit",   "name": "Camera Orbit",     "min": -180.0, "max": 180.0,  "defaultValue": 0.0,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F0" },
      { "id": "cam_tilt",    "name": "Camera Tilt",      "min": -90.0,  "max": 90.0,   "defaultValue": -10.0, "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F0" },
      { "id": "cam_fov",     "name": "Camera FOV",       "min": 20.0,   "max": 120.0,  "defaultValue": 54.0,  "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F0" },
      { "id": "look_y",      "name": "Look Y",           "min": -2.0,   "max": 2.0,    "defaultValue": 0.0,   "wholeNumbers": false, "isToggle": false, "formatString": "F2" }
    ],
    "bindings": [
      { "id": "feedback",    "label": "Feedback",        "defaultValue": 0.98,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "blend_lerp", "param": "amount" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "noise_scale", "label": "Noise Scale",     "defaultValue": 0.75,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "noise_scale_inv", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "noise_speed", "label": "Noise Speed",     "defaultValue": 0.1,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "noise_z_calc", "param": "b" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "edge_str",    "label": "Edge Strength",   "defaultValue": 5.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "edge_gain", "param": "gain" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "mirror",      "label": "Mirror",          "defaultValue": 45.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "mirror_deg_to_rad", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "displace",    "label": "Displace",        "defaultValue": 0.2,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "displace_mesh_node", "param": "displacement" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },
      { "id": "displace",    "label": "Displace",        "defaultValue": 0.2,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "displacement" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "roughness",   "label": "Roughness",       "defaultValue": 0.05,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "roughness" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "light_int",   "label": "Light Intensity", "defaultValue": 3.5,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "light_intensity" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "cam_dist",    "label": "Camera Distance", "defaultValue": 2.5,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "camera_distance" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "cam_orbit",   "label": "Camera Orbit",    "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "cam_orbit_deg_to_rad", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "cam_tilt",    "label": "Camera Tilt",     "defaultValue": -10.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "cam_tilt_deg_to_rad", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "cam_fov",     "label": "Camera FOV",      "defaultValue": 54.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "cam_fov_deg_to_rad", "param": "a" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } },

      { "id": "look_y",      "label": "Look Y",          "defaultValue": 0.0,
        "target": { "kind": "handleNode", "handle": "render", "param": "look_y" },
        "convert": { "type": "Float" } }
    ]
  },
  "nodes": [
    { "id": 0,  "typeId": "system.generator_input", "handle": "input" },

    { "id": 1,  "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "noise_scale_inv",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.75 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },
    { "id": 2,  "typeId": "node.math", "handle": "noise_scale_recip",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }, "op": { "type": "Enum", "value": 3 } } },

    { "id": 3,  "typeId": "node.math", "handle": "noise_z_calc",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "b": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.1 }, "op": { "type": "Enum", "value": 2 } } },

    { "id": 4,  "typeId": "node.simplex_field_2d", "handle": "noise",
      "params": {
        "scale_x":  { "type": "Float", "value": 1.333 },
        "scale_y":  { "type": "Float", "value": 1.333 },
        "offset_x": { "type": "Float", "value": -0.667 },
        "offset_y": { "type": "Float", "value": -0.667 },
        "z":        { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "output_channel": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 }
      } },

    { "id": 5,  "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "noise_scaled",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.3 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.5 } } },

    { "id": 6,  "typeId": "node.feedback", "handle": "fb_color",
      "outputFormats": { "out": "rgba16float" } },

    { "id": 7,  "typeId": "node.mix", "handle": "noise_minus_prev",
      "params": { "amount": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }, "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 5 } } },

    { "id": 8,  "typeId": "node.abs_texture", "handle": "diff_abs" },

    { "id": 9,  "typeId": "node.mix", "handle": "blend_lerp",
      "params": { "amount": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.98 }, "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 } } },

    { "id": 10, "typeId": "node.gaussian_blur", "handle": "blur_h",
      "params": { "kernel_size": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 }, "axis": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 }, "step": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },
    { "id": 11, "typeId": "node.gaussian_blur", "handle": "blur_v",
      "params": { "kernel_size": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 }, "axis": { "type": "Enum", "value": 1 }, "step": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 12, "typeId": "node.brightness", "handle": "luma_for_height" },

    { "id": 13, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "height_remap1",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.7 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.3 } } },
    { "id": 14, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "height_remap2",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.8 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": -0.25 } } },
    { "id": 15, "typeId": "node.clamp_texture", "handle": "height_clamp",
      "params": { "min": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "max": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },
    { "id": 16, "typeId": "node.power_texture", "handle": "height_pow",
      "params": { "exponent": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.8 } } },

    { "id": 17, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "mirror_deg_to_rad",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 45.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.01745329 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },
    { "id": 18, "typeId": "node.mirror_axis", "handle": "mirrored",
      "params": { "angle": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.785398 } } },

    { "id": 19, "typeId": "node.brightness", "handle": "luma_for_sobel" },

    { "id": 20, "typeId": "node.convolution_2d_9tap", "handle": "sobel_x",
      "params": {
        "k0": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 }, "k1": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "k2": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },
        "k3": { "type": "Float", "value": -2.0 }, "k4": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "k5": { "type": "Float", "value": 2.0 },
        "k6": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 }, "k7": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "k8": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },
        "bias": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "normalise": { "type": "Bool", "value": false }
      } },
    { "id": 21, "typeId": "node.convolution_2d_9tap", "handle": "sobel_y",
      "params": {
        "k0": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 }, "k1": { "type": "Float", "value": -2.0 }, "k2": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 },
        "k3": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },  "k4": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },  "k5": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "k6": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },  "k7": { "type": "Float", "value": 2.0 },  "k8": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },
        "bias": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "normalise": { "type": "Bool", "value": false }
      } },

    { "id": 22, "typeId": "node.pack_channels", "handle": "gradient_xy",
      "params": {
        "default_r": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_g": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_b": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_a": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }
      } },

    { "id": 23, "typeId": "node.length_vec2", "handle": "gradient_mag" },

    { "id": 24, "typeId": "node.gain", "handle": "edge_gain",
      "params": { "gain": { "type": "Float", "value": 5.0 } } },

    { "id": 25, "typeId": "node.clamp_texture", "handle": "edge_clamp",
      "params": { "min": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "max": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },

    { "id": 26, "typeId": "node.scale_offset_texture", "handle": "metallic_invert",
      "params": { "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": -1.0 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },
    { "id": 27, "typeId": "node.clamp_texture", "handle": "metallic_clamp",
      "params": { "min": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "max": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 } } },
    { "id": 28, "typeId": "node.power_texture", "handle": "metallic_pow",
      "params": { "exponent": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.5 } } },

    { "id": 29, "typeId": "node.pack_channels", "handle": "packed",
      "params": {
        "default_r": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_g": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_b": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "default_a": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 }
      } },

    { "id": 30, "typeId": "node.feedback", "handle": "fb_processed",
      "outputFormats": { "out": "rgba16float" } },

    { "id": 31, "typeId": "node.mix", "handle": "temporal_blend",
      "params": { "amount": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.15 }, "mode": { "type": "Enum", "value": 0 } } },

    { "id": 32, "typeId": "node.bake_equirect_envmap", "handle": "envmap",
      "params": {
        "width":  { "type": "Int", "value": 512 },
        "height": { "type": "Int", "value": 256 },
        "horizon_strength": { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },
        "azimuth_variation": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.12 }
      } },

    { "id": 33, "typeId": "node.generate_grid_mesh", "handle": "grid_mesh",
      "params": {
        "max_capacity": { "type": "Int", "value": 90000 },
        "resolution_x": { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "resolution_y": { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "size_x":       { "type": "Float", "value": 2.0 },
        "size_y":       { "type": "Float", "value": 2.0 }
      } },

    { "id": 34, "typeId": "node.displace_mesh", "handle": "displace_mesh_node",
      "params": {
        "cols":         { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "rows":         { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "displacement": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.2 },
        "height_bias":  { "type": "Float", "value": 0.5 }
      } },

    { "id": 35, "typeId": "node.triangulate_grid", "handle": "triangulated",
      "params": {
        "src_cols": { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "src_rows": { "type": "Int", "value": 300 }
      } },

    { "id": 36, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "cam_orbit_deg_to_rad",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.01745329 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },
    { "id": 37, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "cam_tilt_deg_to_rad",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": -10.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.01745329 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },
    { "id": 38, "typeId": "node.affine_scalar", "handle": "cam_fov_deg_to_rad",
      "params": { "a": { "type": "Float", "value": 54.0 }, "scale": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.01745329 }, "offset": { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 } } },

    { "id": 39, "typeId": "node.render_3d_mesh_pbr_ibl", "handle": "render",
      "params": {
        "grid_size":          { "type": "Int", "value": 300 },
        "camera_distance":    { "type": "Float", "value": 2.5 },
        "camera_orbit":       { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "camera_tilt":        { "type": "Float", "value": -0.1745 },
        "camera_fov":         { "type": "Float", "value": 0.9425 },
        "look_y":             { "type": "Float", "value": 0.0 },
        "light_x":            { "type": "Float", "value": -2.0 },
        "light_y":            { "type": "Float", "value": 2.0 },
        "light_z":            { "type": "Float", "value": 5.0 },
        "light_intensity":    { "type": "Float", "value": 3.5 },
        "metallic":           { "type": "Float", "value": 1.0 },
        "roughness":          { "type": "Float", "value": 0.05 },
        "displacement":       { "type": "Float", "value": 0.2 },
        "edge_roughness_mul": { "type": "Float", "value": 4.0 },
        "light_color":        { "type": "Color", "value": [1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0] },
        "base_color":         { "type": "Color", "value": [0.8, 0.8, 0.82, 1.0] }
      } },

    { "id": 40, "typeId": "system.final_output", "handle": "final_output" }
  ],
  "wires": [
